data.description: As you enter this well maintained home you'll be greeted by an expansive living space with high ceilings, filled with natural light thanks to large windows and an open floor plan. The kitchen is equipped with SS appliances, granite countertops, decorative lighting, and a huge pantry. The spacious master suite is on the first floor and has a walk-in closet and en-suite bathroom with a large shower and relaxing soaking tub. This home includes a dedicated office space on the first floor. Upstairs, a junior suite and 2 additional bedrooms with a jack and jill bath offer comfort and convenience for family and guests.  The second living area could be a media room, game room, or fitness space. Enjoy the weather on your backyard patio, perfect for outdoor entertaining and overlooking the custom cedar fenced pet area complete with lighting. A spacious two-car garage ensures ample parking and storage. Conveniently located near schools, shopping, and dining with easy access to major highways.
